  Stacey surprised her fans last month when she shared the news that she and husband Joe Swash, 40, were expecting their third child together. Yesterday, the I’m A Celebrity… Get Me Out Of Here! winner showcased her growing baby bump as she posed in a green linen dressing gown. The Sort Your Life Out presenter enjoyed some much-needed pampering in her late stage of pregnancy, treating herself to a dreamy-looking shower after a busy day with her adorable children and cute pups. “Goodnight love from me and my bump,” Stacey told her followers before heading to bed.   